=head1 DESCRIPTION

Pair of two related strings. Allowed characters are letters, white
space, and numbers that can be represented in UTF-8 and the following
characters: C< + - = . _ : />

=head1 ATTRIBUTES


=head2 B<REQUIRED> Key => Str

The tag key (String). The key can't start with C<aws:>.

Length Constraints: Minimum length of 1. Maximum length of 128.

Pattern: C<^(?![aA]{1}[wW]{1}[sS]{1}:)([\p{L}\p{Z}\p{N}_.:/=+\-@]+)$>


=head2 B<REQUIRED> Value => Str

The value of the key.

Length Constraints: Maximum length of 256.

Pattern: C<^([\p{L}\p{Z}\p{N}_.:/=+\-@]*)$>



